data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly desirable northside neighborhood-The Orchards. Upon entering the stunning three-bedroom, two-bathroom home, you will immediately notice the residence is bathed in natural light, creating a bright and airy living space. The open concept design seamlessly blends the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The heart of this home is the modern kitchen, complete with sleek appliances, a huge pantry, and an oversized island. Retreat to the spacious bedrooms, including a master suite with a large walk-in closet and a beautiful floor to ceiling tiled shower. Check out the great sized laundry room that even features a large utility sink. The beautiful interior is complemented by a meticulously maintained landscaped outdoor space. The backyard features a large deck and a huge shed, perfect for extra storage. This home has plenty of incredible updates and even includes a home security system. Don't miss out on on this rare opportunity to own a home that combines elegance, functionality, and ample storage space-it's the complete package!
